edu.brown.cs.ivy.jcomp

Interface JcompSearcher.SearchResult

  • Enclosing interface:
    JcompSearcher

    public static interface JcompSearcher.SearchResult
    This interface represents a file location for a search result. The offset, length and source indicate the location. Where symbol information is available for that location, it is included.
